inistration aid is not accepted by patient.</p>\n</div></blockquote><h3>DosageInstructions</h3><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td style=\"display: none\">-</td><td><b>Text</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"display: none\">*</td><td>1-2 tablets orally every 4-6 hours as needed for pain</td></tr></table><h3>Substitutions</h3><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td style=\"display: none\">-</td><td><b>WasSubstituted</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"display: none\">*</td><td>false</td></tr></table></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
